      8  10000 ????						; Atari VCS Game - Enhanced Version
      9  10000 ????						;------------------------------------------------
     10  10000 ????						; Console Switches Dictionary:
     11  10000 ????						; GAME SELECT:   Cycles starting lives (3, 5, or 1)
     12  10000 ????						; GAME RESET:	  Starts the game (same as Fire button)
     13  10000 ????						; LEFT DIFF:	  P0 Difficulty (A = Fast Monster, B = Normal Monster)
     14  10000 ????						; RIGHT DIFF:	  P1 Difficulty (A = Fast Ball Spawn, B = Normal Ball Spawn)
     15  10000 ????						;------------------------------------------------
